- Consume the file in full, and map against your understanding of the project from prior context.
- Each line must be prepended with `- [ ] YYYY‑MM‑DD: `.
- Should be short, actionable (no paragraphs).
- When task is done, change to `- [x] YYYY‑MM‑DD`.
- Moving or archiving tasks requires adding to context with justification.
